data.title: Maher Zain Lyrics
data.meta_description: Maher Zain Lyrics - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document contains lyrics to Islamic religious songs praising God and the Prophet Muhammad. The songs express love for God and longing to be close to the Prophet. They discuss faith, repentance, family and the promise of paradise. Overall the lyrics promote Islamic spiritual values.
